fields.summary: The user called to order aspirin 75mg for pickup.
fields.transcript:
User: I need aspirin.
Agent: What strength do you need?
User: 75mg, one tablet.
Agent: Perfect, for pickup or delivery?
User: Pickup.
Agent: Your order has been confirmed.

fields.summary: The user called to order medication and successfully placed an order for one tablet of aspirin 75mg for pickup.
fields.transcript:
User: Hello?
Agent: Thank you for calling Curestock. My name is Cimo. How can I help with your medication needs today?
User: I need one active one incident.
Agent: Could you clarify the names of the medications you are referring to? I would be happy to assist with your order!
User: I am sorry. Can you repeat?
Agent: Of course! Could you please provide the names of the medications you need? I will help you place your order right away.
User: Uh, the first medication I need is, uh, aspirin.
Agent: Got it! What strength of aspirin do you need, and how many tablets would you like to order?
User: I need thirty mg.
Agent: Thank you! Unfortunately, aspirin typically comes in strengths like 75mg, 81mg, or 325mg. Could you confirm if you need one of these, or should I check for a specific brand or formulation?
User: Give me seventy five mg.
Agent: Got it! How many tablets of aspirin 75mg would you like to order?
User: I would like to order one one.
Agent: Just to confirm, you would like to order one tablet of aspirin 75mg?
User: Yes.
Agent: Thank you! I have added one tablet of aspirin 75mg to your order. Is there anything else you need today?
User: No. Nothing else. Only this much.
Agent: Great! Let me confirm your order: 1 tablet of aspirin 75mg. Would you prefer delivery or pickup for your order?
User: Pickup.
Agent: Perfect! Your order will be ready for pickup. Thank you for choosing Curestock. Have a great day!
User: Thank you.
Agent: You are very welcome! Take care!
